WEBVTT

00:00.280 --> 00:01.700
Previously on Medium:

00:01.710 --> 00:02.530
Miss Doyle.

00:02.560 --> 00:06.030
I want to help you develop your
solar cell amplification system.

00:06.040 --> 00:09.590
In exchange for funding,
she wants 51% ownership.

00:09.610 --> 00:11.750
Do you want to give up
control of your idea?

00:11.780 --> 00:13.890
- No,of course I don't.
- Then don't.

00:13.900 --> 00:18.450
I'm sorry,but unless you're
willing to rethink the 51/49 split,

00:18.460 --> 00:20.230
I don't see how I can do this with you.

00:20.250 --> 00:22.230
So,how did it go? How'd she take it?

00:22.240 --> 00:24.200
I signed the papers.

00:24.850 --> 00:26.300
Meghan Doyle.

00:26.310 --> 00:27.940
So nice to finally meet you.

00:27.950 --> 00:29.830
Yeah,it's nice to finally meet you.

00:29.840 --> 00:32.040
Well,she's very pretty.

00:32.049 --> 00:34.440
Well,let's try not to
hold that against her.

00:34.450 --> 00:37.170
I just now realized that
I don't have my wallet.

00:37.180 --> 00:38.900
Okay. Miss you.

00:38.910 --> 00:41.690
I thought you were with the boyfriend.

00:41.700 --> 00:43.960
Best-laid plans...

00:43.980 --> 00:47.210
Or not laid, as the case may be.

