01:01.200 --> 01:05.500
That is one sharp lunchbox.

01:05.510 --> 01:07.210
No,seriously.

01:07.230 --> 01:10.550
My brother has one
just like it. He's six.

01:10.560 --> 01:13.140
So,what's your excuse?

01:13.930 --> 01:16.310
Oh,come on,loser.

01:16.320 --> 01:20.170
You know you want to say
something, so just say it.

01:22.800 --> 01:25.840
Yeah. Didn't think so.

01:57.860 --> 02:00.630
Damn,kid. You scared me.

02:00.640 --> 02:03.560
Thought you were Sister Beatrice.

02:05.720 --> 02:08.830
You know if you tell her I'm
out here,you are dead meat.

02:11.530 --> 02:14.470
Kid! I'm talking to you!

02:25.560 --> 02:27.140
No,no...

